# Migration rules

This repo contains:

- /jekyll-geometryclub = read-only reference material from the existing Jekyll site
- the rest of the repo = the new Next.js implementation

Rules:

- Never modify files inside /jekyll-geometryclub
- Use /jekyll-geometryclub to preserve layout, styling, copy, routes, metadata, and asset usage where sensible
- Build all new code in the Next.js app only
- Reuse image assets where possible, but place live assets for the new site in the proper Next.js/public locations
- Do not redesign unless explicitly asked
- Preserve URLs and SEO patterns where possible
- For styling, use CSS Modules for component styling and a small global CSS file for typography and layout defaults.
